mortgages
.
Four hundred and thirty thousand pounds.
No. 5. The Bond of Sir Joseph Job, for
sixty-three
thousand pounds.
I laid down the paper, and involuntarily
exclaimed
,
Property is in danger! Sir Joseph turned
